thread.title: Education software firm Instructure files for IPO
thread.title_full: Education software firm Instructure files for IPO | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Education software firm Instructure files for IPO
text:
Oct 9 Education software company Instructre Inc on Friday filed with U.S. regulators for an initial public offering of common stock.
Morgan Stanley, Goldman Sachs & Co and Jefferies are among the underwriters for the offering, the company said in a filing with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission. ( 1.usa.gov/1WRoKXP ) (Reporting by Kshitiz Goliya in Bengaluru; Editing by Savio D'Souza)
